
# Observed Trends
1) Capomulin and Ramicane treatments reduced the average tumor volume (mm3) by 19% and 22% respectively. All other treatments failed to inhibit tumor growth. 
2) Capomulin and Ramicane treatments were the most effective in preventing the spread of the tumors. The average number of metastatic sites after 45 days was 1.476190 and 1.250000 respectivley.
3) The survival rate for the Capomulin and Ramicane treatments were greater than all other treatment at 84% and 80% respectively.

# for i, v in enumerate(plot_change):

def autolabel(rects):
    """
    Attach a text label above each bar displaying its height
    """
    for rect in rects:
        height = rect.get_height()
        ax.text(rect.get_x() + rect.get_width()/2., 0.2*height,
                '%d%%' % int(height),
                ha='center', va='center', fontweight='bold', color='black')

autolabel(ax1)
autolabel(ax2)
autolabel(ax3)
